data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the desirable Green Valley Ranch neighborhood of Denver, CO on low maintenance corner lot.  This stunning residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and privacy. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a spacious layout, this home is perfect for those seeking a retreat from the bustling city. This home has been well maintained and is practically NEW!

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting living space filled with an abundance of natural light. The interior boasts a bright and airy atmosphere, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance throughout. The main bedroom, located on the second floor, features a walk-in closet, a private bathroom with a double sink vanity, and remodeled custom shower tile. Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a spacious bathroom also on the second floor. Additionally, you will find a huge loft area on the 3rd floor and the 4th bedroom offering privacy and versatility. Either can be used as an office space.

The kitchen is a true highlight of this home, with its oversized island, generous cabinet space, and expansive countertops. Prepare meals with ease and entertain guests effortlessly in this spacious and well-appointed culinary haven. The kitchen also provides convenient access to the backyard, making outdoor dining and entertaining a breeze.

Speaking of the backyard, prepare to be captivated by the gorgeous landscaping that surrounds this home.  Spend your evenings relaxing on the back-stamped concrete patio, enjoying the serene beauty of your own private oasis. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a space to entertain family and friends, great for pets, this backyard has it all.

The HOA removes snow, including the driveway, and takes care of front landscaping, including irrigation.

Great central location in Green Valley Ranch! Walk to Town Center Park & schools. Close to multiple parks, shopping, & dining. Easy drive to DIA & downtown.

Furniture is available for sale.
